summary: An ordinance authorizing an agreement with the United States of America, Forest Service, Dept. of Agriculture, and with Scott Paper Co., Weyerhaeuser Co. and Mountain Tree Farm Co. concerning logging operations, access, and the exchange of lands in the Cedar River Watershed; and modifying and extending to the year 2010 an existing agreement with said private owners of timber in said Watershed.
note: Fiche includes map of Cedar River Watershed land and timber ownership and Cedar River Watershed Cooperative Agreement.
